reviews.text: Well-known Hakka Restaurant, traditional Hakka dishes, original and economy. Waiter and waitress are serving nicely, unlike many other old restaurant  with poor manner. Recommended!
Great natural tasted like mum's cooking & reasonable priced! Worth trying.
Foods are good & prices are fair.
A very nice place to gather

On April 13, 2018, we had dinner in this restaurant. The washing room is extremely dirty, and the waiter's attitude was very bad! It was late in the night so we decided to eat there any way... The waiter first serviced us a soup that we did not realize it was not the one we ordered, so we started to drink the soup. About a minute later  the soup we ordered was ready and he realized he made a mistake, he was very angry at us and grab the soup we have already drink and pour back to the serve bowl. To my big surprise, he served the bowl of the soup that we have already drink to the other table!!! Stay away from this restaurant.

reviews.text: 往這處只因長途是問題！打听下，原來大廚曾任職馬會！怪不得每樣菜亦甚有水準！10款菜15人吃，平均每位270圓。並且其中包含有250元是貼士。這消費合理。
老飯店的味道還能保持著，灣仔區午餐不錯的選擇
鹽焗雞飯，及雞湯飯最正！牛腩钣夠味！午市不二之選！！！
D嘢又唔係好食。一路食，一路俾佢地d伙計催住，一路趕住執我地d碗碟，跟住催住要我地埋單。又唔係全場爆滿，又唔係有客排隊等位，場內還有幾張空枱，一路想趕客快d埋單走人。 咁嘅服務態度，我以後都唔會再幫趁。我亦會反對一切我認識嘅人幫趁灣仔呢間垃圾食肆。
Well-known Hakka Restaurant, traditional Hakka dishes, original and economy. Waiter and waitress are serving nicely, unlike many other old restaurant  with poor manner. Recommended!
